Transcript: Agent: Hello, main Aryan hoon Trimfinity se. Maine dekha ki aapne product cart mein add kiya tha. Aaj ke din aapke liye additional 5% off hai. Kya aap ise claim karna chahenge?
CallSummary: The agent, Aryan from Trimfinity, reached out to the user to inform them about an additional 5% discount on a product they added to their cart. The call aimed to encourage the user to claim the discount.
